            <title>[FLINK-17943] HiveFunctionWrapper#getUDFClass should use Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-17943</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;HiveFunctionWrapper#getUDFClass&lt;/tt&gt; currently uses &lt;tt&gt;Class.forName(className)&lt;/tt&gt; to load Hive UDF classes, while &lt;tt&gt;HiveFunctionWrapper#createFunction&lt;/tt&gt; uses &lt;tt&gt;Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;HiveFunctionWrapper#getUDFClass&lt;/tt&gt; should also use &lt;tt&gt;Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader()&lt;/tt&gt; as it is loading user classes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
